OL,3,CGovernment announces new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle small boat crossings
OL,6,FThis follows a 50% increase in the
OL,7,Fnumber of NCA officers stationed at
OL,8,FEuropol, which is currently conducting
OL,9,Faround 70 active investigations into
OL,10,Fpeople smuggling and trafficking
OL,11,Fgroups.
OL,13,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said the
OL,14,Fofficers have been swiftly deployed to
OL,15,Fsupport European operations targeting
OL,16,Fcriminal smuggling gangs profiting
OL,17,Ffrom small boat crossings.
