OL,6,FShe assured that a range of sanctions,
OL,7,Fincluding financial penalties,
OL,8,Fbusiness closure orders, and potential
OL,9,Fprosecution, will be imposed on
OL,10,Femployers of illegal workers.
OL,12,FThere will also be a significant
OL,13,Fincrease in enforcement and
OL,14,Fdeportation flights, aiming to reach
OL,15,Fthe highest removal levels since 2018,
OL,16,Freversing the recent decline.
OL,18,FDetention capacity will be expanded
OL,19,Fwith 290 additional beds at Campsfield
OL,20,Fand Haslar Immigration Removal Centres.
