OL,4,Ctackle small boat crossings
OL,6,FThis increase aims to provide the
OL,7,Fadditional space needed to support
OL,8,Fhigher levels of enforcement and
OL,9,Freturns, ensuring that immigration
OL,10,Frules are properly enforced.
OL,12,FStaff will be redeployed to support
OL,13,Fthe increased returns, which have
