OL,6,F"And by increasing enforcement
OL,7,Fcapabilities and returns, we will
OL,8,Festablish a system that is better
OL,9,Fcontrolled and managed, in place of
OL,10,Fthe chaos that has blighted the system
OL,11,Ffor far too long."
OL,13,FHome Office figures showed 206
OL,14,Fmigrants crossed the English Channel
OL,15,Fin three boats on Monday, which has
OL,16,Ftaken the 2024 provisional total
OL,17,Fcrossings to 19,294.
OL,19,FThis is a 10% increase on the figure
OL,20,Frecorded last year, which was 17,620.
